com.inqwell.any

Class ArrayMessageFormat

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.text.Format
      • java.text.MessageFormat
        • com.inqwell.any.ArrayMessageFormat
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    public class ArrayMessageFormat
extends MessageFormat
    This is a wrapper around the standard java.text.MessageFormat class to support strings parameterised by an array of Any values. The original functionality is unchanged except that the appropriate methods from java.text.MessageFormat are provided to ensure that instances of AnyFormat are installed where appropriate.
